name: check user dashboard after login
fullName: child support login functionality: check user dashboard after login

steps.name: When I enter valid email and password for worksheet
And I click the login button for worksheet
Then Wait for the parent element of the dropdown to be visible and Scroll to the worksheet dropdown parent and click
Then Wait until the dropdown options are visible and click the "Create Worksheet" option
When I fill the details in the first page
And I click add child button and add child details
And click on Gross income schedule A
When I redirect to Gross income schedule A and fill the gross income details
And I click the save worksheet button
And I enter the description and click save
